<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Document</title>
    <style>
        body: {
            color: black;
        }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div style="width: 100%; background-image: url('cid:background'); background-repeat: no-repeat;">
      <img src="cid:logo" width="400px" style="display: flex; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; padding-top: 100px;" />
      <div style="width: 45%; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;">
        <p>
          Dear {{name}},
        </p>

        <p>
          We’re sleigh-riding into your inbox with some jingle-bell jolly news! You’ve been paired by the elves (aka our algorithm) for this year’s Secret Santa extravaganza! 🎄✨
        </p>

        <p>
          Now, don’t get your tinsel in a tangle, because we’ve got everything you need to be the best Secret Santa ever. We’ve checked our list (twice, of course) and found the perfect match for you! Drumroll, please… 🥁
        </p>

        <p>
          Your Secret Santa recipient is {{personName}}! 🎉
        </p>

        <p>
          Remember, the spirit of Secret Santa is not just in the gifts, but in the mystery and joy of giving! So, keep your identity under wraps like a well-wrapped present until the big reveal. 🎅🏻🕵️
        </p>

        <p>
          You have until {{eventDate}} to find the perfect present. But don’t wait until you hear reindeer on your roof – start your holiday mission now!
        </p>

        <p>
          Let’s make this holiday season the most fa-la-la-la-fabulous one yet! 🌟
        </p>

        <p>
          Happy Secret Santa-ing!
        </p>
      </div>
  </body>
</html>
